        <abstract> 
<p>Appleton &amp; Co. wish to be supplied with set of stereotype plates of CD’s new book [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] for American market; will pay for cost of plates, and 10% of sales to CD.</p>  
<p>Also desire plates for new edition of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>.</p> 
